Protein - slows food from stomach to intestine
Fibre - insoluble and soluble - expands with water (vegetables, fruits, whole grains, legumes)
Any food with high water content

Make sure that with every meal there is a good balance between protein, carbs, fat and fibre.
Filling foods
Mushy peas
Potatoes with skins
Don't eat sugar
Replace bran flakes with all bran (all bran less sugar, lower GI index)
